WorkItem.Description:
Version 1.7.1
 
Error:
Strict standards: Only variables should be passed by reference in Classes/PHPExcel/Reader/CSV.php on line 142
 
In the line:
"$probableDelimiter = array_shift(array_flip($delimiterCount));"
 
array_shift requires a variable as argument - solution is to use an intermediary variable.

Comments.Message: Use the latest PHPExcel (the unstable source code version), delimiter detection is now removed from PHPExcel_Reader_CSV::canRead, because it never worked too well. See http://phpexcel.codeplex.com/WorkItem/View.aspx?WorkItemId=10897 for details.
Ah thank you, I will see if I can use that version instead.
